  A[2026-04-12 старт] --> B[0-2 недели\nRTK-001 actor->AuthContext\nRTK-003 body limits\nRTK-005 typed errors\nRTK-009 guardrails]
  B --> C[2-8 недель\nRTK-004 artifact storage\nRTK-006 cancellation/supervisor\nRTK-007 bounded rate limiter\nRTK-008 cached settings]
  C --> D[2-6 месяцев\nRTK-002 split public/internal routers\nThreat modeling + security test pack]
